reviewText: I Love The Edited DB Series! That Aired In The 90's On Cartoon Network's Toonami And Saturday Mornings On The Fox Kids Network! I Like The Fox Kids Network 1!
This is the Classic Dragonball Ocean Dub that was originally aired on Toonami back in the mid 90's ! I recommend this for hardcore Fans Only !
The review title says it all. DO NOT buy this is you're seeking uncut, quality Dragon Ball. If you have a multi-region player, import the Region 4 Uncut DVD of the first 13 episodes.
